---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import { getLangFromUrl, useTranslations } from "../../i18n";

const lang = "en";
const t = useTranslations(lang);
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - LUMIA"
  description="Privacy policy of LUMIA Specialized Dentistry. Learn how we protect your personal information."
  lang={lang}
  keywords="privacy policy, data protection, LUMIA, privacy policy"
>
  <Header />

  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section
      class="relative h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden"
    >
      <div class="absolute inset-0">
        <img
          src="/optimized-images/img-lumia-ultra/equipo-trabajo-2-optimized.webp"
          alt="LUMIA Clinic"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale brightness-50"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/40"></div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="relative z-10 text-center text-white max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"
      >
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light mb-8 tracking-wide">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-2xl mb-12 opacity-90 font-light tracking-wide"
        >
          How we protect and manage your personal data
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Privacy Content Section -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
            LUMIA ODONTOLOGÍA S.A.S., in development of its corporate purpose
            related to the provision of general and specialized dentistry
            services, guarantees proper handling of personal data in accordance
            with the Constitutional Habeas Data guarantee established in Law
            1581 of 2012.
          </p>

          {/* Legal Framework */}
          <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">
              Legal Framework
            </h3>
            <ul class="text-gray-700">
              <li>• Colombian Constitution (Articles 15 and 20)</li>
              <li>• Law 1581 of 2012 and Decree 1377 of 2013</li>
              <li>• Decree 1074 of 2015</li>
              <li>• Resolution 839 of 2017 from Ministry of Health</li>
              <li>• Law 2015 of 2020 and Resolution 1888 of 2025</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          {/* Data Controller Information */}
          <div class="bg-amber-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-amber-900 mb-4">
              Data Processing Controller Identification
            </h3>
            <div class="text-gray-700">
              <p>
                <strong>Company:</strong> LUMIA ODONTOLOGÍA S.A.S.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Tax ID:</strong> 901.823.286-1
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Address:</strong> Calle 33B #20-03 Local 9909, Manizales
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Phones:</strong> 606 8902828 - 3164052829
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> lumiaodontologia@gmail.com / lumiagestion01@gmail.com
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong>Website:</strong> www.lumiaodontologia.com
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          {/* Processing Principles */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Processing Principles
          </h3>
          <ol class="text-gray-600 mb-4 list-decimal pl-6">
            <li>
              <strong>Legality:</strong> Data processing is regulated and subject
              to current law.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Purpose:</strong> Data is processed for legitimate, previously
              informed purposes.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Freedom:</strong> Requires prior, express, and informed consent
              from the data subject.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Truthfulness or Quality:</strong> Information must be truthful,
              complete, accurate and up-to-date.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Transparency:</strong> Guarantee the data subject's right to
              obtain information.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Security:</strong> Protect information against tampering, loss
              or unauthorized access.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Confidentiality:</strong> Maintain confidentiality by those
              who process the data.
            </li>
          </ol>

          {/* Authorization */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Authorization for Data Processing
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            The collection, storage, use, circulation and processing of personal
            data requires the <strong
              >free, prior, express and informed consent</strong
            >
            of the data subjects.
          </p>

          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            <strong>Authorization can be granted through:</strong>
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
            <li>Physical or electronic documents</li>
            <li>Data messages or email</li>
            <li>
              Any digital format that allows guaranteeing subsequent
              consultation
            </li>
            <li>Unambiguous conduct of the data subject</li>
          </ul>

          {/* Processing Purposes */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Processing Purposes
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            LUMIA ODONTOLOGÍA S.A.S. processes personal data for the following
            purposes:
          </p>
          <ol class="text-gray-600 mb-4 list-decimal pl-6">
            <li>
              Analysis of treated population and delivery of RIPS to control
              agencies
            </li>
            <li>
              Update, programming and confirmation of appointment processes
            </li>
            <li>
              Sending information about promotions, events and oral health
              campaigns
            </li>
            <li>Evaluation of the quality of treatments and services</li>
            <li>Virtual monitoring of dental treatment evolution</li>
            <li>Compliance with legal and contractual obligations</li>
            <li>Commercial due diligence</li>
            <li>Commercial communication and marketing</li>
            <li>Compliance with commercial and labor obligations</li>
            <li>Depersonalized statistical analysis</li>
            <li>Security and fraud prevention purposes</li>
          </ol>

          {/* Data Subject Rights */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Data Subject Rights
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            As a data subject, you have the following rights:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-gray-600 mb-4 list-disc pl-6">
            <li>
              <strong>Know, update and rectify</strong> your personal data
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Request proof</strong> of the authorization granted
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Be informed</strong> about how your data has been used
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>File complaints</strong> with the Superintendency of Industry
              and Commerce
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Revoke authorization</strong> and request data deletion
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Access your personal data free of charge</strong>
            </li>
          </ul>

          {/* Exercise of Rights (ARCO) */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Exercise of Rights (ARCO)
          </h3>
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">
              For queries and requests:
            </h4>
            <ul class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
              <li>
                • <strong>Queries:</strong> Answered within maximum 10 business days
              </li>
              <li>
                • <strong>Claims:</strong> Answered within maximum 15 business days
              </li>
              <li>
                • <strong>Contact:</strong> WhatsApp 3164052829
              </li>
              <li>
                • <strong>Web Form:</strong> www.lumiaodontologia.com/privacidad
              </li>
              <li>
                • <strong>Email:</strong> lumiaodontologia@gmail.com / lumiagestion01@gmail.com
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          {/* Clinical Records */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Clinical Records and Health Data
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Clinical records will be kept for a minimum period of <strong
              >15 years</strong
            >
            counted from the date of the last care, in accordance with Resolution
            839 of 2017 from the Ministry of Health. Health-related data are considered
            <strong>sensitive data</strong>
            and require express authorization from the data subject.
          </p>

          {/* Security */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Security Measures
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            We implement technical, human and administrative measures to protect
            your personal data against tampering, loss, consultation, use or
            unauthorized or fraudulent access. Any security incident will be
            reported to the competent authorities.
          </p>

          {/* Minors' Data */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Processing of Minors' Data
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            Processing personal data of minors requires authorization from the
            legal representative and assessment of the minor's opinion according
            to their maturity and understanding capacity.
          </p>

          {/* Digital Channels */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Digital Channels
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            For data processing through website, applications and WhatsApp, we
            implement digital privacy notices, cookie management and technical
            mechanisms for exercising rights.
          </p>

          {/* Final Contact */}
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">
            Contact
          </h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
            To exercise your rights or for questions about this policy, you can
            contact us through:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <strong>LUMIA ODONTOLOGÍA S.A.S.</strong><br />
              <strong>Tax ID:</strong> 901.823.286-1<br />
              Calle 33B #20-03 Local 9909<br />
              Manizales, Caldas, Colombia<br />
              <strong>Phones:</strong> 606 8902828 / 3164052829<br />
              <strong>Email:</strong> lumiaodontologia@gmail.com<br />
              <strong>Website:</strong> www.lumiaodontologia.com<br />
              <strong>Form:</strong> www.lumiaodontologia.com/privacidad
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg mt-8">
            <p class="text-gray-800">
              <strong>Effective Date:</strong> This policy is effective as of September
              24, 2025.<br />
              <strong>Version:</strong> 2.0 (Update Addendum)
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
